name: COMMONWEALTH of Pennsylvania, Respondent, v. Steven P. GREEN, Petitioner

parties: COMMONWEALTH of Pennsylvania, Respondent, v. Steven P. GREEN, Petitioner.

opinions.text:
ORDER
PER CURIAM.
AND NOW, this 5th day of June 2002, the Petition for Allowance of Appeal is granted, the order of the Superior Court is reversed, and the matter is remanded to the trial court with direction to grant Petitioner an appeal nunc pro tunc.
opinions.author: PER CURIAM.

attorneys: Francis J. Schultz, Meadille, for Commonwealth of Pennsylvania.
casebody.head_matter:
798 A.2d 202
COMMONWEALTH of Pennsylvania, Respondent, v. Steven P. GREEN, Petitioner.
Supreme Court of Pennsylvania.
June 5, 2002.
Steven P. Green, Pro Se.
Francis J. Schultz, Meadille, for Commonwealth of Pennsylvania.
